body:
Extracted from #27138 to make that PR smaller and so that people who are having trouble building this package (me) can build it immediately.

@tgamblin this is another case of a package where separate concretization of build deps is required just to build. Modern TF requires newer Bazel than WIT supports. Same problem affects `py-jupyter-packaging`.

Successfully installs on macOS 10.15.7 with Python 3.9.9 and Apple Clang 12.0.0.
